channel.title: Rimmington Powercutter
channel.description:
I would like to buy a Rimmington Powercutter that cuts all of the willow logs down south, then when full, it goes to the general store a bit northwest and sell the logs to the store owner. After that it drops the gold you recieved to the ground and proceed woodcutting. I would like to have it do all of the randoms and then drop the item it gives you. Also all of the basic materials for the script such as picking the axe head, running from ent, etc.
I am willing to pay for this script, just give me a price and we will deal with it.
Thank You Very Much...
